{"tid":200242,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企隻寵物試過有結膜炎?","createTime":"2017-04-13T18:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:27:42.000Z","uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6f8e6031681c04f7e2b482df9300fb27046df51b","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T18:56:11.000Z","msg":"喺上個星期三我發現我屋企隻倉鼠眼球下方紅咗，一開始以為眼花睇錯 因為都幾唔明顯下<br />\n<br />\n然後隔日(上星期四)再睇發現真喺紅咗，就決定等星期五朝早打電話去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但最快都要等到星期一<br />\n<br />\n到星期一果陣 ，醫生話我隻倉鼠喺白內障惡化成結膜炎，之後開左枝含有類固醇成份嘅眼藥水比佢<br />\n話可以幫佢消炎同舒緩惡化速度 叫我一日幫佢滴一滴 咁我就按照幫佢滴 喺滴完15-30分鐘後 有明顯微微消腫 但眼依舊紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  藥散會腫得更加明顯<br />\n之後都冇理到 滴多日觀察下 點知都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問有冇人屋企寵物試過有結膜炎？<br />\n大概幾耐會好番？同埋會唔會同我一樣藥散會更加腫？另外想問如果我停藥唔滴類固醇副作用會唔會發出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你想講倉鼠唔值救 咁平 死咗買過隻懇求你唔好留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45df4ce208bd0f02d58265b09f4c6e9c76007b0c","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T04:29:43.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79d8335b0e26383a168c59f83ed721444a5ab8f","tid":200242,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T06:52:21.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f12e8db181302c939f2ef3fa6382164ca9ff8d","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83096b9a3ae588631920c3a991783420db16bab","tid":200242,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"幾多歲"},{"pid":"85fa2ca1b7371cc1284feb71aa29dc425b66a0f3","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多歲</blockquote><br />\n1歲2個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57311501a42664acb580d5bbfc34a2320e5c171c","tid":200242,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主最後點？睇左邊個醫生？"},{"pid":"251d1b40c741ea84a2dcf3525d6baef338b107b4","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57311501a42664acb580d5bbfc34a2320e5c171c","tid":200242,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主最後點？睇左邊個醫生？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"最後睇咗荃灣享和楊醫生<br />\n醫生開咗啲眼藥水比佢滴"},{"pid":"d8412bfc01668e55b45aa181f78e9560d81b1949","tid":200242,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"251d1b40c741ea84a2dcf3525d6baef338b107b4","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57311501a42664acb580d5bbfc34a2320e5c171c","tid":200242,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主最後點？睇左邊個醫生？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"最後睇咗荃灣享和楊醫生<br />\n醫生開咗啲眼藥水比佢滴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"咁有冇睇過楓樹珍禽異獸？<br />\n<br />\n我隻鼠兩邊眼都有發炎，睇過一間滴左眼藥水好返d，之後又發炎過，想去試下楓樹，享和太遠"},{"pid":"2934069e057e8421d94287f5e5c9fea930e4ad78","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8412bfc01668e55b45aa181f78e9560d81b1949","tid":200242,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"251d1b40c741ea84a2dcf3525d6baef338b107b4","tid":200242,"uid":67105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"